summary:
**Operational Update Summary (Blackjack Gold Project):**  
- **First gold pour on track for end-July 2025**; dry commissioning of processing plant underway.  
- **Key milestones achieved**:  
  - Plant energization completed; wet commissioning to follow.  
  - Tailings Storage Facility (TSF) pre-discharge works 90% complete (final embankment lifts by end-June).  
  - Open pit development advanced, with first ore delivery to ROM pad expected early July.  
- **Resource drilling**: ~10,000m completed to support pit design and grade control.  

**No material financial or capital structure impacts disclosed.**  

*(Note: Excludes routine operational details and forward-looking statements.)*
